_sText:
This is my first published map.
I hope you like it.
I worked on this map for 1-2 months.
There are 15 Traps, 2 Ends, 10 Porn nades, 51 spawns (49 ct's - 7x7 and 2 t's).
One of the traps is from an other map but only because one of the members asked for it.
I'm sorry for that.
I build all on my own.
I didn't steal any work from other maps.

Important !!!
If the gravity is 718 or lower, the t's can jump up to the weapons at the end. If it's 719 or higher it's ok.

Have fun at playing !
